  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abstractanks is an action-packed real-time-strategy game with an abstract neon theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play <strong>intense multiplayer</strong> skirmishes with up to 16 players or AIs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beat the <strong>short, handcrafted single-player campaign</strong> and master <strong>tough optional challenges</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Capture spawn circles to quickly produce <strong>hundreds of units</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your map-control to collect and unleash game-changing <strong>power-ups</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Switch the <strong>only unit type</strong> between damage- and utility-mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Climb the leaderboards on <strong>procedurally generated maps</strong> in the endless horde mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Freely <strong>shape your units</strong> into any formation or split units with simple and intuitive controls.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abstractanks is an action-packed real-time-strategy game with an abstract neon theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play <strong>intense multiplayer</strong> skirmishes with up to 16 players or AIs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beat the <strong>short, handcrafted single-player campaign</strong> and master <strong>tough optional challenges</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Capture spawn circles to quickly produce <strong>hundreds of units</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your map-control to collect and unleash game-changing <strong>power-ups</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Switch the <strong>only unit type</strong> between damage- and utility-mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Climb the leaderboards on <strong>procedurally generated maps</strong> in the endless horde mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Freely <strong>shape your units</strong> into any formation or split units with simple and intuitive controls.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
